snippet: The police did not know of a motive for the killing of Dune Janelle Jacobs, who was shot in a corner of the northern part of the borough that saw a spike in violence this year.
abstract: Bronx woman Dune Janelle Jacobs is shot and killed on East 213th Street near White Plains Road; killing is 17th this year for 47th Precinct, which has seen more homicides this year than any other part of city.
lead_paragraph: The police did not know of a motive for the killing of Dune Janelle Jacobs, who was shot in a corner of the northern part of the borough that saw a spike in violence this year.

headline.main: Bronx Woman, 31, Is Fatally Shot in the Head
headline.print_headline: Bronx Woman, 31, Fatally Shot in Head
